'''industry_density''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the frequency of industries for a new map.<br><br>
0 = no industries, only by funding<br>
1 = minimal<br>
2 = very low<br>
3 = low<br>
4 = normal<br>
5 = high (default)<br>
<pre>
[difficulty]
industry_density = 5
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 ]

'''Default:''' 5


